event: The key following key(s) were pressed: ['\uffc0'].
description: The user pressed the '\uffc0' key, which in Corel WordPerfect 7 corresponds to the "End" key. As a result, the cursor moved to the end of the current line, changing to a right-pointing arrow to indicate its position at the line's end.
outcome: The time displayed in the status bar has updated to "2:55 PM". The mouse cursor has moved near the right edge of the editing area and changed to a right-pointing arrow. All other elements of the UI remain unchanged.

event: The key following key(s) were pressed: ['￣', 'o'].
description: The user pressed the keyboard shortcut "Ctrl+O". As a result, the right margin, previously hidden, became visible as a blue dotted line in the Corel WordPerfect 7 document window.
outcome: The only change observed in the UI is that the right margin, represented by a blue dotted line, has become visible in the Corel WordPerfect 7 document window. The cursor is no longer visible.
